    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In Christi nomine amen. Breve ob presentis et futuri temporis memoriam
                        qualiter factum est apud <rs key="#Castle">castrum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/3210">Putei</placeName> et ante domum
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Coloni/tenants #Hospitals"
                                ><rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> Altepascensis</orgName>, et
                        presentia <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum
                        nomina subter scripta repiuntur (sic). <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name
                                ref="Bernardus">Bernardus</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> per virgam (…) fecit
                        finem, diffinitionem, transactionem sive refutationem <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> Dei gratia rectori
                        hospitalis de <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altepascio</placeName> de omnibus illis terris cultis et incultis seu
                        vineis atque arboribus seu casis et cassinis seu casalinis atque nemoribus
                        quas dictus Bernardus per <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">colonariam
                            conditionem</rs> detinebat a dicto Dominico rectore seu a dicto
                        hospitali de Altepascio, in aliquibus locis vel vocabulis. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: quinque librarum puri argenti. (…) Unde
                        predictus Dominicus rector dicti hospitalis nomine meriti dedit eidem
                        Bernardo anulum aureum et insuper liberavit eum a colonaria conditione. (…)
                        Quod actum est anno nativitate Christi millesimo centesimo septuagesimo
                        octavo, pridie kal. octubris, indictione duodecima, et presentia <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Pothatellus"
                                >Buthatelli</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Burrarre"
                                >Burrarre</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                                >Lanfranchi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Renovardus"
                                >Renovardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Malagalgia">Malagalie</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Mainettus"
                                >Mainetti</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Bei"
                                >Bei</name></persName> et aliorum plurium rogatorum <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (L) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Leonardus">Leonardus</name></persName> domni imperatoris
                            <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> predicti omnibus interfui. Ideo hoc
                        causa memorie <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
